  <section class="page-hero"><div class="container page-hero-content"><span class="badge">Serving Lichfield remotely</span><h1>A digital marketing agency for Lichfield ecommerce brands.</h1><p>Spires Digital is run from Guernsey and works remotely with ecommerce businesses in Lichfield, Staffordshire and across the UK. We do not claim a Lichfield office; we provide connected paid media, SEO, CRO, retention and analytics support with direct senior contact.</p><div class="page-hero-actions"><a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Request a growth review</a><a href="/tools/growth-assessment" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Take the free assessment</a></div></div></section>
  <section class="section surface"><div class="container split"><div class="split-copy"><span class="eyebrow">The useful distinction</span><h2>Choose for fit and evidence—not a borrowed local address.</h2><p>A nearby postcode does not guarantee better ecommerce decisions. The practical questions are whether your partner understands margin, can connect the full customer journey and will work transparently inside the accounts you own.</p><p>Our work is structured for remote delivery from our <a href="/locations/guernsey">Guernsey operating base</a>: direct senior contact, shared priorities, recorded decisions and reporting tied to commercial outcomes. Lichfield is service coverage only; Spires Digital does not claim an office there.</p></div><div class="card"><div class="card-body"><h3>One connected remit</h3><ul class="check-list"><li>Google Shopping and paid search</li><li>Meta advertising and creative testing</li><li>Ecommerce SEO and content architecture</li><li>Shopify CRO and customer journeys</li><li>Email retention and lifecycle</li><li>Affiliate management</li><li>Analytics and attribution</li></ul></div></div></div></section>
  <section class="section surface-warm"><div class="container"><div class="section-heading"><span class="eyebrow">A practical first step</span><h2>Pressure-test the numbers yourself.</h2><p>Our free planning tools work in your browser and do not require an email address.</p></div><div class="grid grid-3"><a class="card" href="/tools/ecommerce-profit-calculator"><div class="card-body"><h3>Profit &amp; ROAS calculator</h3><p>Turn store economics into acquisition guardrails.</p></div></a><a class="card" href="/tools/channel-budget-planner"><div class="card-body"><h3>Channel budget planner</h3><p>Work backwards from revenue to orders, traffic and spend.</p></div></a><a class="card" href="/tools/paid-media-waste-estimator"><div class="card-body"><h3>Waste estimator</h3><p>Create an investigation range for your paid accounts.</p></div></a></div></div></section>
